<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/x-icon" href="favicon.ico"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="favicon-32.png"/>
  <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="192x192" href="favicon-192.png"/>
  <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="favicon-192.png"/>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Pedido recebido · Raio de Sol Pipas</title>
<meta name="robots" content="noindex"/>
<style>
  :root{ --accent:#3B82F6; --text:#1A2050; --muted:#64748B; --bg:#F0F7FF; }
  *{box-sizing:border-box}
  body{margin:0;min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:24px;
       background:var(--bg);font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;color:var(--text)}
  .card{background:#fff;max-width:480px;width:100%;border-radius:24px;padding:48px 36px;text-align:center;
        box-shadow:0 20px 60px -20px rgba(10,14,39,.25)}
  .check{width:84px;height:84px;border-radius:50%;background:#DCFCE7;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin:0 auto 24px}
  .check svg{width:44px;height:44px;color:#16A34A}
  h1{font-size:26px;margin:0 0 10px}
  p{color:var(--muted);font-size:15px;line-height:1.6;margin:0 0 8px}
  .pedido{display:none;margin:18px auto 6px;padding:8px 16px;background:var(--bg);border-radius:10px;
          font-family:ui-monospace,SFMono-Regular,Menlo,monospace;font-size:13px;color:var(--text)}
  .actions{margin-top:30px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:12px}
  .btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 24px;border-radius:12px;
       font-weight:700;font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;transition:transform .15s,background .2s}
  .btn-primary{background:var(--accent);color:#fff}
  .btn-primary:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);background:#2563EB}
  .btn-ghost{background:transparent;color:var(--muted);border:1px solid #E2E8F0}
  .btn-ghost:hover{border-color:var(--accent);color:var(--accent)}
  .zap{margin-top:26px;font-size:13px;color:var(--muted)}
  .zap a{color:#16A34A;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none}
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="check">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/></svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Pedido recebido!</h1>
    <p>Obrigado pela compra. Assim que o pagamento for confirmado, preparamos seu pedido para envio.</p>
    <div class="pedido" id="num-pedido"></div>
    <p style="font-size:13px">Se você pagou no PIX, a confirmação costuma ser rápida.</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="index.html">Voltar à loja</a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="catalogo.html">Ver catálogo</a>
    </div>
    <p class="zap">Dúvidas sobre seu pedido? <a href="https://wa.me/5594984361103" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Chama no WhatsApp</a></p>
  </div>

  <script>
    // Compra concluída: limpa o carrinho.
    try { localStorage.removeItem('rs_carrinho'); } catch (e) {}

    // Se a Infinity Pay devolver o número do pedido na URL, mostra.
    try {
      var p = new URLSearchParams(location.search);
      var num = p.get('order_nsu') || p.get('order_id') || p.get('pedido') || '';
      if (num) {
        var el = document.getElementById('num-pedido');
        el.textContent = 'Pedido ' + num;
        el.style.display = 'inline-block';
      }
    } catch (e) {}
  </script>
</body>
</html>
